description: This file defines the AIMLApi class, a subclass of OpenAILike, for interfacing with models hosted on AIMLApi. It includes attributes for model configuration and a method to format messages by replacing None content with an empty string.

classes.name: AIMLApi
classes.description: A class for using models hosted on AIMLApi, extending OpenAILike, with specific attributes and a message formatting method.

methods.name: _format_message
methods.description: Formats a Message object into a dictionary, replacing None content with an empty string.
